@graph.creator: Common Data Model Builder
@graph.description: Data model specification documenting both individual-level  data required to respond to the three (3) research questions related to the hip fracture persona in ICCONIC. The data model specification includes the cohort definition (shared across the 3 studies), individual-level model specification for each of the 3 studies including data dictionaries and crosswalks for semantic interoperable definition of certain variables (i.e. socioeconomic groups, clinical conditions and comorbidities - (def)). See below some of the conventions used to document this data model
